He leans over toward ELLIE.

				JUD
		Who might you be, little Miss?

				ELLIE
		I'm Ellen Creed and I live at 642
		Alden Lane, Dearborn, Michigan. (Pause)
		At least, I used to.

				JUD
		And now you live on Route 9 in Ludlow,
