He hurries in.

EXT.  ELIIE, ON THE DEADFALL

She looks back at JUD.

				ELLIE
		It's okay, Mr. Crandall--

EXT.  ELLIE'S FOOT, CU

The branch she's on breaks with a dry CRRRACK. Her foot drops down 
suddenly.

EXT.  ELLIE AND JUD

She totters backward, pinwheeling her arms, and JUD catches her as 
