INT.  LOUIS, IN THE LIVING ROOM  NIGHT

He's on the phone, smiling and happy.

				RACHEL (voice)
		You want to talk to the birthday girl?

				LOUIS
		That'd be real fine.

				ELLIE (voice)
		Hi...daddy?

				LOUIS (sings)
